{"id": "anc_tab_underline", "modality": "animations", "name": "Tab Underline", "task": {"description": "Create a self-contained 1920x1080 HTML animation (inline CSS, NO <canvas>) of a horizontal tab bar with FIVE equally-spaced tab labels and a sliding underline indicator. Over ~4s the active tab cycles 1->2->3->4->5, and the underline slides to sit exactly under the active tab each time (matching its width and x-position).", "requirements": ["Five tab labels in one evenly-spaced horizontal row, fully within the viewport at every frame", "A single underline indicator is present and sits directly under exactly one tab at each settled moment", "The active tab changes over time (1 through 5)", "The underline's horizontal position changes over time to track the active tab", "The underline stays on the tab-bar axis (never drifts above/below the row or off the sides)", "The underline width matches the tab it underlines (does not overshoot into neighbors)"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2138, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 2111}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2216, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 2100}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2205, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 2192}], "ss_img": "images/animations/anc_tab_underline_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/animations/anc_tab_underline_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Sliding Tab Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .tab-container {\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            padding: 40px;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n        }\n\n        .tab-bar {\n            position: relative;\n            display: flex;\n            width: 800px;\n            height: 80px;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            padding: 8px;\n            box-shadow: inset 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .tab {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #6c757d;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .tab.active {\n            color: #495057;\n        }\n\n        .tab-underline {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 8px;\n            height: 4px;\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #667eea, #764ba2);\n            border-radius: 2px;\n            transition: all 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        /* Animation keyframes for the underline */\n        @keyframes slideUnderline {\n            0% {\n                left: 8px;\n                width: 148px;\n            }\n            20% {\n                left: 164px;\n                width: 148px;\n            }\n            40% {\n                left: 320px;\n                width: 148px;\n            }\n            60% {\n                left: 476px;\n                width: 148px;\n            }\n            80%, 100% {\n                left: 632px;\n                width: 148px;\n            }\n        }\n\n        .tab-underline {\n            animation: slideUnderline 4s ease-in-out infinite;\n        }\n\n        /* Tab active state animation */\n        .tab:nth-child(1) { animation: tabActive1 4s ease-in-out infinite; }\n        .tab:nth-child(2) { animation: tabActive2 4s ease-in-out infinite; }\n        .tab:nth-child(3) { animation: tabActive3 4s ease-in-out infinite; }\n        .tab:nth-child(4) { animation: tabActive4 4s ease-in-out infinite; }\n        .tab:nth-child(5) { animation: tabActive5 4s ease-in-out infinite; }\n\n        @keyframes tabActive1 {\n            0%, 20% { color: #495057; font-weight: 700; }\n            21%, 100% { color: #6c757d; font-weight: 600; }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes tabActive2 {\n            0%, 19% { color: #6c757d; font-weight: 600; }\n            20%, 40% { color: #495057; font-weight: 700; }\n            41%, 100% { color: #6c757d; font-weight: 600; }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes tabActive3 {\n            0%, 39% { color: #6c757d; font-weight: 600; }\n            40%, 60% { color: #495057; font-weight: 700; }\n            61%, 100% { color: #6c757d; font-weight: 600; }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes tabActive4 {\n            0%, 59% { color: #6c757d; font-weight: 600; }\n            60%, 80% { color: #495057; font-weight: 700; }\n            81%, 100% { color: #6c757d; font-weight: 600; }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes tabActive5 {\n            0%, 79% { color: #6c757d; font-weight: 600; }\n            80%, 100% { color: #495057; font-weight: 700; }\n        }\n\n        .title {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 32px;\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #2d3748;\n            letter-spacing: -0.5px;\n        }\n\n        .subtitle {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 48px;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #718096;\n            font-weight: 400;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"tab-container\">\n        <h1 class=\"title\">Navigation Tabs</h1>\n        <p class=\"subtitle\">Watch the active indicator slide between tabs</p>\n        \n        <div class=\"tab-bar\">\n            <div class=\"tab\">Dashboard</div>\n            <div class=\"tab\">Analytics</div>\n            <div class=\"tab\">Projects</div>\n            <div class=\"tab\">Settings</div>\n            <div class=\"tab\">Profile</div>\n            <div class=\"tab-underline\"></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Sliding Tab Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .tab-container {\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            padding: 40px;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n        }\n\n        .tab-bar {\n            position: relative;\n            display: flex;\n            width: 800px;\n            height: 80px;\n            background: #f8fafc;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            padding: 8px;\n            box-shadow: inset 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .tab {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #64748b;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n        }\n\n        .tab.active {\n            color: #3b82f6;\n        }\n\n        .tab-underline {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 8px;\n            left: 8px;\n            height: 4px;\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #1d4ed8);\n            border-radius: 2px;\n            transition: all 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        /* Animation keyframes for tab cycling */\n        @keyframes slideUnderline {\n            0% {\n                width: 148px;\n                transform: translateX(0px);\n            }\n            20% {\n                width: 148px;\n                transform: translateX(156px);\n            }\n            40% {\n                width: 148px;\n                transform: translateX(312px);\n            }\n            60% {\n                width: 148px;\n                transform: translateX(468px);\n            }\n            80% {\n                width: 148px;\n                transform: translateX(624px);\n            }\n            100% {\n                width: 148px;\n                transform: translateX(0px);\n            }\n        }\n\n        .tab-underline {\n            width: 148px;\n            animation: slideUnderline 4s infinite ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        /* Tab active state animation */\n        .tab:nth-child(1) { animation: tabActive1 4s infinite; }\n        .tab:nth-child(2) { animation: tabActive2 4s infinite; }\n        .tab:nth-child(3) { animation: tabActive3 4s infinite; }\n        .tab:nth-child(4) { animation: tabActive4 4s infinite; }\n        .tab:nth-child(5) { animation: tabActive5 4s infinite; }\n\n        @keyframes tabActive1 {\n            0%, 20% { color: #3b82f6; }\n            20.1%, 100% { color: #64748b; }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes tabActive2 {\n            0%, 20% { color: #64748b; }\n            20.1%, 40% { color: #3b82f6; }\n            40.1%, 100% { color: #64748b; }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes tabActive3 {\n            0%, 40% { color: #64748b; }\n            40.1%, 60% { color: #3b82f6; }\n            60.1%, 100% { color: #64748b; }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes tabActive4 {\n            0%, 60% { color: #64748b; }\n            60.1%, 80% { color: #3b82f6; }\n            80.1%, 100% { color: #64748b; }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes tabActive5 {\n            0%, 80% { color: #64748b; }\n            80.1%, 100% { color: #3b82f6; }\n        }\n\n        .title {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #1e293b;\n            letter-spacing: -0.5px;\n        }\n\n        .subtitle {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #64748b;\n            font-weight: 500;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"tab-container\">\n        <h1 class=\"title\">Sliding Tab Navigation</h1>\n        \n        <div class=\"tab-bar\">\n            <div class=\"tab\">Dashboard</div>\n            <div class=\"tab\">Analytics</div>\n            <div class=\"tab\">Projects</div>\n            <div class=\"tab\">Settings</div>\n            <div class=\"tab\">Profile</div>\n            <div class=\"tab-underline\"></div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <p class=\"subtitle\">Watch the indicator slide between tabs</p>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}